<br>
What you're referring to was mentioned in the article I referenced yesterday, but I can't find it today.  Anyway, there won't be stats to be figured at 1st level.  You won't choose your players skills.  They intend for there to be only three attributes, Skill, knowledge, and arts.<br>
<br>
Knowledge, I think, is what will affect item decay.  I might be wrong though.  They mentioned it specifically and said that a low level player would be able to USE high end gear, but they would be MUCH more likely to break it than a high level player.<br>
<br>
Hopefully, they will also code in some sort of EPIC flag to make items that do NOT decay, as some things you just shouldn't have to worry about.<br>
<br>
